column1: PEP- Trending nicely along the double sma support and upward wedge. This will see 143 within 1-2 month. Strong support around 136 and if I were to play a debit spread personally 136 to 140. Bull put spread would be the same. PEP could test 140 upper trendline resistance this week or consolidate around 136-139 for this week.

PINS- exploding off the last weeks 41 bottom call to 45+ I wouldn‚Äôt be surprised to see this near 50 end of the week . Realistically must touch 46 then 48. Safety play would be 41 -43 debit spread or a bull put from 41-44. I think this is a generally safe play by end of the week with good volume.
ZM- most likely will test 500$ this week as it confirmed a good support around 480. If you are looking to play this best to debit spread around huge support 480.
WMT- look for a potential entry around 139-140. Long term 150+ but short term it needs consolidate a bit. November or later debit spreads I would recommend just incase of a pull back."
